msgstr "Introduïu els detalls de la targeta"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:282
msgid ""
"Input your current balance and APR (interest rate) from your statement."
msgstr ""
"Introduïu el vostre saldo actual i TAE (taxa d'interès) del vostre extracte."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:288
msgid "Choose Your Goal"
msgstr "Tria el teu objectiu"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:289
msgid ""
"Select how you want to pay: fixed amount, target date, or minimum payments."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu com voleu pagar: import fix, data objectiu o pagaments mínims."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:295
msgid "Compare Strategies"
msgstr "Compara estratègies"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:296
msgid ""
"See how different payment amounts affect your payoff time and interest."
msgstr ""
"Vegeu com els diferents imports de pagament afecten el vostre temps de "
"pagament i els vostres interessos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:308
msgid "Why is paying only the minimum bad?"
msgstr "Per què pagar només el mínim és dolent?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:314
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Minimum payments are designed to maximize interest for the credit card "
"company. A $5,000 balance at 20%% APR with minimum payments could take 20+ "
"years to pay off and cost over $8,000 in interest."
msgstr ""
"Els pagaments mínims estan dissenyats per maximitzar l'interès de l'empresa "
"de la targeta de crèdit. Un saldo de 5.000 dòlars amb un TAE del 20% amb "
"pagaments mínims podria trigar més de 20 anys a pagar-se i costar més de "
"8.000 dòlars en interessos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:320
msgid "What is APR?"
msgstr "Què és l'APR?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:326
msgid ""
"APR (Annual Percentage Rate) is the yearly interest rate on your credit "
"card. It's divided by 12 to calculate monthly interest. Find your APR on "
"your credit card statement or online account."
msgstr ""
"TAE (Taxa percentual anual) és la taxa d'interès anual de la vostra targeta "
"de crèdit. Es divideix per 12 per calcular l'interès mensual. Trobeu la "
"vostra TAE a l'extracte de la targeta de crèdit o al compte en línia."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:332
msgid "How can I pay off debt faster?"
msgstr "Com puc pagar el deute més ràpidament?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:338
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Pay more than the minimum, make extra payments when possible, consider "
"balance transfer cards with 0%% intro APR, or use the debt avalanche "
"(highest rate first) or snowball (smallest balance first) methods."
msgstr ""
"Pagueu més del mínim, feu pagaments addicionals quan sigui possible, "
"considereu targetes de transferència de saldo amb un TAE d'introducció del "
"0%% o utilitzeu els mètodes d'allau de deute (primer la taxa més alta) o "
"bola de neu (primer el saldo més petit)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:344
msgid "Should I use savings to pay off credit cards?"
msgstr "He d'utilitzar els estalvis per pagar les targetes de crèdit?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:350
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Generally yes, if your credit card APR (typically 15-25%%) exceeds your "
"savings interest (typically 0.5-5%%). However, keep an emergency fund of at "
"least $1,000 before aggressively paying debt."
msgstr ""
"En general, sí, si la TAE de la vostra targeta de crèdit (normalment "
"15-25%%) supera els vostres interessos d'estalvi (normalment 0,5-5%%). "
"Tanmateix, mantingueu un fons d'emergència d'almenys 1.000 dòlars abans de "
"pagar el deute de manera agressiva."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:358
msgid "Debt Payoff Tips"
msgstr "Consells de pagament del deute"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:364
msgid "Pay more than the minimum - even $20 extra makes a big difference."
msgstr ""
"Pagueu més del mínim: fins i tot 20 dòlars addicionals fan una gran "
"diferència."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:370
#, python-format
msgid "Consider a balance transfer to a 0%% APR card if you have good credit."
msgstr ""
"Penseu en una transferència de saldo a una targeta TAE del 0%% si teniu un "
"bon crèdit."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:376
msgid ""
"Stop using the card while paying it off to avoid increasing the balance."
msgstr ""
"Deixeu d'utilitzar la targeta mentre la pagueu per evitar augmentar el "
"saldo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Call your card company to ask for a lower interest rate - it often works!"
msgstr ""
"Truqueu a l'empresa de la vostra targeta per demanar un tipus d'interès més "
"baix; sovint funciona!"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:498
msgid "Making only minimum payments will take"
msgstr "Només caldrà fer pagaments mínims"

