#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:260
msgid "What is LTV?"
msgstr "Què és LTV?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:262
msgid ""
"Loan-to-Value (LTV) is the loan amount divided by the property price. A "
"higher deposit reduces LTV and can help you access better rates."
msgstr ""
"Loan-to-Value (LTV) és l'import del préstec dividit pel preu de la "
"propietat. Un dipòsit més alt redueix el LTV i us pot ajudar a accedir a "
"millors tarifes."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:269
msgid "Mortgage Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmules hipotecàries"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:273
msgid "Loan = Property Price − Deposit"
msgstr "Préstec = Preu de la propietat − Fiança"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:276
msgid "Repayment (monthly payment)"
msgstr "Reemborsament (pagament mensual)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:280
msgid "Interest-only (monthly payment)"
msgstr "Només interessos (pagament mensual)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:284
msgid ""
"Where P is loan amount, r is monthly interest rate (annual rate ÷ 12), and n"
" is number of months."
msgstr ""
"On P és l'import del préstec, r és el tipus d'interès mensual (taxa anual ÷ "
"12) i n és el nombre de mesos."

