msgid "Lean Body Mass (LBM)"
msgstr "Massa corporal magra (LBM)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:345
msgid ""
"Your total body weight minus all fat. This includes muscles, bones, organs, "
"and water. Higher LBM generally indicates better body composition."
msgstr ""
"El teu pes corporal total menys tot el greix. Això inclou músculs, ossos, "
"òrgans i aigua. LBM més alt generalment indica una millor composició "
"corporal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:351
msgid ""
"The total weight of fat in your body. Calculated as a percentage of your "
"total weight."
msgstr ""
"El pes total del greix del teu cos. Calculat com a percentatge del teu pes "
"total."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:355
msgid "LBM Percentage"
msgstr "Percentatge de LBM"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"The percentage of your total weight that is lean body mass. Higher "
"percentages indicate better body composition."
msgstr ""
"El percentatge del vostre pes total que és massa corporal magra. "
"Percentatges més alts indiquen una millor composició corporal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:361
msgid "Protein Recommendations"
msgstr "Recomanacions de proteïnes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:363
msgid ""
"Based on your LBM and activity level. Sedentary individuals need less "
"protein, while athletes and bodybuilders need more to support muscle "
"maintenance and growth."
msgstr ""
"En funció del vostre LBM i nivell d'activitat. Les persones sedentàries "
"necessiten menys proteïnes, mentre que els atletes i els culturistes "
"necessiten més per donar suport al manteniment i creixement muscular."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:371
msgid "Body Composition Categories"
msgstr "Categories de composició corporal"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:374
#, python-format
msgid "Essential Fat: &lt; 6%%"
msgstr "Greixos essencials: &lt; 6%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:376
msgid ""
"The minimum amount of fat necessary for basic physical and physiological "
"health. Typically only seen in competitive bodybuilders."
msgstr ""
"La quantitat mínima de greix necessària per a la salut física i fisiològica "
"bàsica. Normalment només es veu en culturistes competitius."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:380
#, python-format
msgid "Athletic: 6-14%%"
msgstr "Atletisme: 6-14%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Excellent body composition typical of athletes. Associated with optimal "
"performance and health."
msgstr ""
"Excel·lent composició corporal típica dels esportistes. Associat amb un "
"rendiment i salut òptims."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:386
#, python-format
msgid "Fitness: 14-18%%"
msgstr "Fitness: 14-18%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"Good body composition for fitness enthusiasts. Indicates a healthy balance "
"of muscle and fat."
msgstr ""
"Bona composició corporal per als amants del fitness. Indica un equilibri "
"saludable de múscul i greix."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:392
#, python-format
msgid "Average: 18-25%%"
msgstr "Mitjana: 18-25%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:394
msgid ""
"Average body composition. Consider incorporating strength training and a "
"balanced diet to improve."
msgstr ""
"Composició corporal mitjana. Penseu en incorporar entrenament de força i una"
" dieta equilibrada per millorar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:398
#, python-format
msgid "Above Average: ≥ 25%%"
msgstr "Per sobre de la mitjana: ≥ 25%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Body fat percentage is above average. Focus on strength training, cardio, "
"and a balanced diet."
msgstr ""
"El percentatge de greix corporal està per sobre de la mitjana. Centra't en "
"l'entrenament de força, el cardio i una dieta equilibrada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:414
msgid ""
"This calculator requires an accurate body fat percentage measurement. Use "
"body fat scales, calipers, DEXA scan, or other professional methods."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta calculadora requereix una mesura precisa del percentatge de greix "
"corporal. Utilitzeu bàscules de greix corporal, pinces, exploració DEXA o "
"altres mètodes professionals."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:420
msgid ""
"LBM includes water weight, which can fluctuate. For more accurate muscle "
"mass tracking, consider using additional methods like DEXA scans."
msgstr ""
"LBM inclou el pes de l'aigua, que pot fluctuar. Per obtenir un seguiment més"
" precís de la massa muscular, considereu l'ús de mètodes addicionals com ara"
" exploracions DEXA."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:426
msgid ""
"Protein recommendations are general guidelines. Individual needs may vary "
"based on goals, training intensity, and other factors."
msgstr ""
"Les recomanacions de proteïnes són pautes generals. Les necessitats "
"individuals poden variar en funció dels objectius, la intensitat de "
"l'entrenament i altres factors."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Consult with healthcare professionals or registered dietitians for "
"personalized nutrition and fitness advice."
msgstr ""
"Consulteu amb professionals sanitaris o dietistes registrats per obtenir "
"consells personalitzats sobre nutrició i fitness."

