#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:325
msgid "What are Macronutrients?"
msgstr "Què són els macronutrients?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:327
msgid ""
"Macronutrients (macros) are the three main nutrients your body needs in "
"large amounts: protein, carbohydrates, and fats. Each provides energy "
"(calories) and serves unique functions in your body."
msgstr ""
"Els macronutrients (macro) són els tres nutrients principals que el cos "
"necessita en grans quantitats: proteïnes, hidrats de carboni i greixos. "
"Cadascun proporciona energia (calories) i compleix funcions úniques al teu "
"cos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:330
msgid "Total Calories = Protein + Fat + Carbs"
msgstr "Calories totals = proteïnes + greixos + carbohidrats"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:333
msgid ""
"Protein and carbohydrates provide 4 calories per gram, while fat provides 9 "
"calories per gram. Understanding your macro breakdown helps you optimize "
"your diet for your specific goals."
msgstr ""
"Les proteïnes i els carbohidrats aporten 4 calories per gram, mentre que el "
"greix aporten 9 calories per gram. Entendre el vostre desglossament macro us"
" ajuda a optimitzar la vostra dieta per als vostres objectius específics."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:339
msgid "Macronutrient Functions"
msgstr "Funcions dels macronutrients"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:342
msgid "Protein (4 cal/g)"
msgstr "Proteïna (4 cal/g)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:344
msgid ""
"Essential for muscle building, repair, and maintenance. Supports immune "
"function, hormone production, and satiety. Recommended: 0.8-2.2g per kg body"
" weight depending on activity level."
msgstr ""
"Essencial per a la construcció, reparació i manteniment muscular. Afavoreix "
"la funció immune, la producció d'hormones i la sacietat. Recomanat: 0,8-2,2 "
"g per kg de pes corporal segons el nivell d'activitat."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:348
msgid "Fat (9 cal/g)"
msgstr "Greix (9 cal/g)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:350
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Provides energy, supports hormone production, aids vitamin absorption, and "
"protects organs. Essential for brain health. Recommended: 20-35%% of total "
"calories."
msgstr ""
"Aporta energia, dóna suport a la producció d'hormones, ajuda a l'absorció de"
" vitamines i protegeix els òrgans. Imprescindible per a la salut del "
"cervell. Recomanat: 20-35%% del total de calories."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:354
msgid "Carbohydrates (4 cal/g)"
msgstr "Hidrats de carboni (4 cal/g)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:356
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Primary energy source for your body and brain. Supports exercise performance"
" and recovery. Recommended: 45-65%% of total calories for most people, lower"
" for low-carb diets."
msgstr ""
"Font d'energia primària per al teu cos i cervell. Afavoreix el rendiment i "
"la recuperació de l'exercici. Recomanat: 45-65%% del total de calories per a"
" la majoria de la gent, més baix per a dietes baixes en carbohidrats."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:366
msgid ""
"Enter your total daily calorie target (use a TDEE calculator if unsure)"
msgstr ""
"Introduïu el vostre objectiu total de calories diàries (utilitzeu una "
"calculadora TDEE si no esteu segur)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:367
msgid "Use quick presets or manually adjust macro percentages using sliders"
msgstr ""
"Utilitzeu ajustos predefinits ràpids o ajusteu manualment els percentatges "
"de macro mitjançant controls lliscants"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:368
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Ensure percentages sum to 100%% (the calculator will warn you if they don't)"
msgstr ""
"Assegureu-vos que els percentatges sumin al 100%% (la calculadora us avisarà"
" si no ho fan)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:369
msgid "Click 'Calculate Macros' to see your breakdown"
msgstr "Feu clic a \"Calcula les macros\" per veure el vostre desglossament"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:370
msgid "Review the charts and meal distribution recommendations"
msgstr "Reviseu els gràfics i les recomanacions de distribució dels àpats"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:371
msgid "Adjust percentages based on your goals and preferences"
msgstr ""
"Ajusteu els percentatges en funció dels vostres objectius i preferències"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:377
msgid "Common Macro Splits"
msgstr "Macro Splits comuns"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:380
#, python-format
msgid "Balanced: 30%% Protein, 30%% Fat, 40%% Carbs"
msgstr "Equilibrat: 30%% proteïnes, 30%% greixos, 40%% carbohidrats"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Standard balanced diet suitable for most people. Good for general health and"
" maintenance."
msgstr ""
"Dieta equilibrada estàndard adequada per a la majoria de la gent. Bo per a "
"la salut general i el manteniment."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:386
#, python-format
msgid "High Protein: 40%% Protein, 30%% Fat, 30%% Carbs"
msgstr "Alt en proteïnes: 40%% proteïnes, 30%% greixos, 30%% carbohidrats"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"Ideal for muscle building, weight loss with muscle preservation, and "
"increased satiety."
msgstr ""
"Ideal per a la construcció muscular, pèrdua de pes amb preservació muscular "
"i augment de la sacietat."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:392
#, python-format
msgid "Low Carb: 35%% Protein, 40%% Fat, 25%% Carbs"
msgstr "Baix en carbohidrats: 35%% proteïnes, 40%% greixos, 25%% carbohidrats"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:394
msgid ""
"Reduced carbohydrate intake. Good for weight loss, blood sugar control, and "
"some athletes."
msgstr ""
"Reducció de la ingesta d'hidrats de carboni. Bo per a la pèrdua de pes, el "
"control del sucre en la sang i alguns atletes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:398
#, python-format
msgid "Ketogenic: 20%% Protein, 70%% Fat, 10%% Carbs"
msgstr "Cetogènic: 20%% proteïnes, 70%% greixos, 10%% carbohidrats"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Very low carbohydrate, high fat diet. Promotes ketosis. Requires careful "
"planning and monitoring."
msgstr ""
"Dieta molt baixa en carbohidrats i alta en greixos. Afavoreix la cetosi. "
"Requereix una planificació i un seguiment acurats."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"The actual amount in grams you should consume daily. Use this for meal "
"planning and tracking."
msgstr ""
"La quantitat real en grams que hauríeu de consumir diàriament. Utilitzeu-ho "
"per planificar i fer el seguiment dels àpats."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:417
msgid "Macro Calories"
msgstr "Macro calories"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"The calories contributed by each macronutrient. These should sum to your "
"total daily calories."
msgstr ""
"Les calories aportades per cada macronutrient. Aquests haurien de sumar el "
"total de calories diàries."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:425
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Suggested breakdown across meals: Breakfast (25%%), Lunch (35%%), Dinner "
"(30%%), Snacks (10%%). Adjust based on your schedule and preferences."
msgstr ""
"Desglossament suggerit entre àpats: esmorzar (25%%), dinar (35%%), sopar "
"(30%%), aperitius (10%%). Ajusteu-vos en funció del vostre horari i "
"preferències."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:439
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Macro percentages must sum to exactly 100%%. The calculator will warn you if"
" they don't."
msgstr ""
"Els percentatges de macro han de sumar exactament el 100%. La calculadora us"
" avisarà si no ho fan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:445
msgid ""
"Optimal macro splits vary based on goals, activity level, body composition, "
"and individual preferences."
msgstr ""
"Les divisions macro òptimes varien en funció dels objectius, el nivell "
"d'activitat, la composició corporal i les preferències individuals."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:451
msgid ""
"Meal distribution is a suggestion. Adjust timing based on your schedule, "
"training, and preferences."
msgstr ""
"La distribució dels àpats és una proposta. Ajusteu el temps en funció del "
"vostre horari, formació i preferències."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:457
msgid ""
"Consult with registered dietitians or nutritionists for personalized macro "
"recommendations, especially for specific health conditions."
msgstr ""
"Consulteu amb dietistes o nutricionistes registrats per obtenir "
"recomanacions macro personalitzades, especialment per a condicions de salut "
"específiques."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:518
#, python-format
msgid "Percentages must sum to 100%%"
msgstr "Els percentatges han de sumar el 100%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:23
