msgstr "Greix (30%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:359
msgid "Current Activity Level"
msgstr "Nivell d'activitat actual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:380
msgid "What is TDEE?"
msgstr "Què és TDEE?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Total Daily Energy Expenditure (TDEE) is the total number of calories your "
"body burns in a day. It includes your Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR) plus the "
"calories burned through physical activity, digestion, and other daily "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"La despesa energètica diària total (TDEE) és el nombre total de calories que"
" el cos crema en un dia. Inclou la vostra taxa metabòlica basal (BMR) més "
"les calories cremades amb l'activitat física, la digestió i altres "
"activitats diàries."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:385
msgid ""
"TDEE is calculated by multiplying your BMR (the calories your body needs at "
"rest) by an activity multiplier that accounts for your daily physical "
"activity level."
msgstr ""
"El TDEE es calcula multiplicant el teu BMR (les calories que el teu cos "
"necessita en repòs) per un multiplicador d'activitat que té en compte el teu"
" nivell d'activitat física diària."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:388
msgid "TDEE = BMR × Activity Multiplier"
msgstr "TDEE = BMR × Multiplicador d'activitat"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:394
msgid "What is BMR?"
msgstr "Què és BMR?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:396
msgid ""
"Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR) is the number of calories your body burns at rest"
" to maintain basic physiological functions like breathing, circulation, cell"
" production, and brain function. It represents the minimum energy needed to "
"keep your body alive."
msgstr ""
"La taxa metabòlica basal (BMR) és el nombre de calories que el teu cos crema"
" en repòs per mantenir les funcions fisiològiques bàsiques com la "
"respiració, la circulació, la producció cel·lular i la funció cerebral. "
"Representa l'energia mínima necessària per mantenir viu el teu cos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:399
#, python-format
msgid ""
"BMR accounts for 60-75%% of your total daily calorie burn. It's calculated "
"using formulas that consider your age, gender, height, and weight."
msgstr ""
"La BMR representa el 60-75%% de la vostra crema diària total de calories. Es"
" calcula mitjançant fórmules que tenen en compte la teva edat, sexe, alçada "
"i pes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:405
msgid "Activity Levels Explained"
msgstr "Nivells d'activitat explicats"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:408
msgid "Sedentary (1.2x)"
msgstr "Sedentari (1,2x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:410
msgid ""
"Little or no exercise. Office job, minimal physical activity. Mostly sitting"
" or lying down."
msgstr ""
"Poc o gens d'exercici. Treball d'oficina, activitat física mínima. "
"Majoritàriament assegut o estirat."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:414
msgid "Light Activity (1.375x)"
msgstr "Activitat de llum (1.375x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:416
msgid ""
"Light exercise 1-3 days per week. Walking, light jogging, or recreational "
"activities. Light physical work."
msgstr ""
"Exercici lleuger 1-3 dies per setmana. Caminar, córrer lleugerament o "
"activitats recreatives. Treball físic lleuger."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:420
msgid "Moderate Activity (1.55x)"
msgstr "Activitat moderada (1,55x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:422
msgid ""
"Moderate exercise 3-5 days per week. Regular workouts, sports, or active "
"lifestyle. Moderate physical work."
msgstr ""
"Exercici moderat 3-5 dies per setmana. Entrenaments regulars, esports o "
"estil de vida actiu. Treball físic moderat."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:426
msgid "Active (1.725x)"
msgstr "Actiu (1.725x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:428
msgid ""
"Hard exercise 6-7 days per week. Intense workouts, competitive sports, or "
"physically demanding job."
msgstr ""
"Exercici dur 6-7 dies per setmana. Entrenaments intensos, esports de "
"competició o feina físicament exigent."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:432
msgid "Very Active (1.9x)"
msgstr "Molt actiu (1,9x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Very hard exercise, physical job. Daily intense exercise or physically "
"demanding work. Multiple training sessions."
msgstr ""
"Exercici molt dur, treball físic. Exercici intens diari o treball físicament"
" exigent. Múltiples sessions d'entrenament."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:438
msgid "Athlete (2.0x)"
msgstr "Atleta (2.0x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:440
msgid ""
"Professional athlete level. Multiple daily training sessions, competition "
"preparation, extremely high activity level."
msgstr ""
"Nivell esportista professional. Múltiples sessions d'entrenament diàries, "
"preparació de competició, nivell d'activitat extremadament alt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:451
msgid "Select your gender (affects BMR calculation)"
msgstr "Seleccioneu el vostre gènere (afecta el càlcul de BMR)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:452
msgid "Enter your age (between 15 and 80 years)"
msgstr "Introdueix la teva edat (entre 15 i 80 anys)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:453
msgid "Enter your height and weight"
msgstr "Introduïu la vostra alçada i pes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:455
msgid "Click 'Calculate TDEE' to see your results"
msgstr "Feu clic a \"Calcula TDEE\" per veure els vostres resultats"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:467
msgid ""
"The calories your body burns at complete rest. This is your baseline "
"metabolic rate, representing the minimum energy needed for basic body "
"functions."
msgstr ""
"Les calories que el teu cos crema en repòs complet. Aquesta és la vostra "
"taxa metabòlica de referència, que representa l'energia mínima necessària "
"per a les funcions bàsiques del cos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:473
msgid ""
"Your total daily calorie burn including all activities. This is the number "
"of calories you need to maintain your current weight. To lose weight, eat "
"below TDEE; to gain weight, eat above TDEE."
msgstr ""
"La teva crema diària total de calories incloses totes les activitats. "
"Aquesta és la quantitat de calories que necessiteu per mantenir el vostre "
"pes actual. Per baixar de pes, menja per sota del TDEE; per augmentar de "
"pes, menja per sobre de TDEE."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:479
msgid ""
"Different calorie levels for various goals. A deficit of 500 calories per "
"day typically results in about 1 pound (0.45 kg) of weight loss per week. A "
"surplus of 500 calories per day typically results in about 1 pound of weight"
" gain per week."
msgstr ""
"Diferents nivells de calories per a diferents objectius. Un dèficit de 500 "
"calories al dia normalment provoca una pèrdua de pes d'una lliura (0,45 kg) "
"per setmana. Un excedent de 500 calories al dia normalment provoca un "
"augment de pes d'aproximadament 1 lliura per setmana."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:483
msgid "Macro Recommendations"
msgstr "Recomanacions de macro"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:485
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Suggested macronutrient breakdown (30%% protein, 40%% carbs, 30%% fat) for "
"your TDEE. These percentages can be adjusted based on your specific goals "
"and preferences."
msgstr ""
"Desglossament suggerit de macronutrients (30%% de proteïnes, 40%% de "
"carbohidrats, 30%% de greix) per al vostre TDEE. Aquests percentatges es "
"poden ajustar en funció dels vostres objectius i preferències específiques."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:499
msgid ""
"These are estimates. Actual calorie needs can vary based on genetics, muscle"
" mass, medical conditions, medications, and other individual factors."
msgstr ""
"Aquestes són estimacions. Les necessitats calòriques reals poden variar en "
"funció de la genètica, la massa muscular, les condicions mèdiques, els "
"medicaments i altres factors individuals."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:505
msgid ""
"Be honest about your activity level. Overestimating activity can lead to "
"consuming too many calories, while underestimating can lead to too few "
"calories."
msgstr ""
"Sigues honest sobre el teu nivell d'activitat. Sobreestimar l'activitat pot "
"conduir a consumir massa calories, mentre que subestimar pot provocar massa "
"poques calories."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:511
msgid ""
"For weight loss, a deficit of 250-500 calories per day is typically "
"sustainable. Extreme deficits (>1000 calories) are not recommended without "
"medical supervision."
msgstr ""
"Per a la pèrdua de pes, un dèficit de 250-500 calories al dia normalment és "
"sostenible. Els dèficits extrems (>1000 calories) no es recomana sense "
"supervisió mèdica."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:517
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical or nutritional advice. Always consult with qualified "
"healthcare providers or registered dietitians for personalized nutrition "
"guidance, especially if you have medical conditions, are taking medications,"
" or have specific dietary needs."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta calculadora només té finalitats informatives i no ha de substituir "
"l'assessorament mèdic o nutricional professional. Consulteu sempre amb "
"proveïdors d'atenció mèdica qualificats o dietistes registrats per obtenir "
"orientació nutricional personalitzada, especialment si teniu afeccions "
"mèdiques, preneu medicaments o teniu necessitats dietètiques específiques."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:523
msgid ""
"TDEE can change over time as your weight, muscle mass, and activity level "
"change. Recalculate periodically to ensure accuracy."
msgstr ""
"El TDEE pot canviar amb el temps a mesura que canvien el vostre pes, massa "
"muscular i nivell d'activitat. Recalculeu periòdicament per garantir la "
"precisió."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:741
msgid "Extreme Gain"
msgstr "Guany Extrem"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:5
