#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:307
msgid "What are Weight Watchers SmartPoints?"
msgstr "Què són els SmartPoints de Weight Watchers?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:309
msgid ""
"Weight Watchers SmartPoints is a point system that assigns values to foods "
"based on their nutritional content. Unlike simple calorie counting, "
"SmartPoints considers calories, saturated fat, sugar, and protein to "
"encourage healthier food choices."
msgstr ""
"Weight Watchers SmartPoints és un sistema de punts que assigna valors als "
"aliments en funció del seu contingut nutricional. A diferència del simple "
"recompte de calories, SmartPoints considera calories, greixos saturats, "
"sucre i proteïnes per fomentar opcions d'aliments més saludables."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:312
msgid ""
"Foods higher in calories, saturated fat, and sugar have more points, while "
"foods higher in protein have fewer points. This system helps guide you "
"toward nutrient-dense foods that support weight loss and healthy eating."
msgstr ""
"Els aliments més calories, greixos saturats i sucre tenen més punts, mentre "
"que els aliments més alts en proteïnes tenen menys punts. Aquest sistema us "
"ajuda a guiar-vos cap a aliments densos en nutrients que afavoreixen la "
"pèrdua de pes i una alimentació saludable."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:318
msgid "SmartPoints Formula"
msgstr "Fórmula SmartPoints"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:320
msgid ""
"The SmartPoints formula calculates points based on four nutritional factors:"
msgstr ""
"La fórmula SmartPoints calcula els punts en funció de quatre factors "
"nutricionals:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:324
msgid ""
"Points = (Calories ÷ 33) + (Saturated Fat ÷ 4) + (Sugar ÷ 9) - (Protein ÷ "
"10)"
msgstr ""
"Punts = (Calories ÷ 33) + (Greixos saturats ÷ 4) + (Sucre ÷ 9) - (Proteïna ÷"
" 10)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:328
msgid "Divided by 33. Higher calories = more points."
msgstr "Dividit per 33. Més calories = més punts."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:329
msgid "Divided by 4. Higher saturated fat = more points."
msgstr "Dividit per 4. Major greix saturat = més punts."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:330
msgid "Divided by 9. Higher sugar = more points."
msgstr "Dividit per 9. Més sucre = més punts."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:331
msgid ""
"Divided by 10 and subtracted. Higher protein = fewer points (reduces total "
"points)."
msgstr ""
"Es divideix per 10 i es resta. Major proteïna = menys punts (redueix el "
"total de punts)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:339
msgid ""
"Your daily points allowance is personalized based on your age, gender, "
"height, weight, and activity level. Typical daily allowances range from 23 "
"to 71 points."
msgstr ""
"La teva quantitat diària de punts es personalitza en funció de la teva edat,"
" sexe, alçada, pes i nivell d'activitat. Les dietes típiques oscil·len entre"
" 23 i 71 punts."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:342
msgid ""
"In addition to daily points, Weight Watchers members also receive weekly "
"points (typically 14-28 points) that can be used throughout the week for "
"special occasions or treats."
msgstr ""
"A més dels punts diaris, els membres de Weight Watchers també reben punts "
"setmanals (normalment 14-28 punts) que es poden utilitzar durant tota la "
"setmana per a ocasions especials o llaminadures."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:348
msgid "Understanding Points Status"
msgstr "Entendre l'estat dels punts"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:351
#, python-format
msgid "Excellent (≤50%% of allowance)"
msgstr "Excel·lent (≤50%% del subsidi)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:353
msgid ""
"You're well within your daily points allowance. Great job making healthy "
"choices! You have plenty of points remaining for the day."
msgstr ""
"Estàs dins dels teus punts diaris. Gran feina fent eleccions saludables! Et "
"queden molts punts per al dia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:357
#, python-format
msgid "Good (50-75%% of allowance)"
msgstr "Bé (50-75%% de la prestació)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:359
msgid ""
"You're doing well staying within your points budget. Keep up the good work! "
"You still have a good amount of points remaining."
msgstr ""
"Esteu fent bé mantenint-vos dins del vostre pressupost de punts. Seguiu "
"així! Encara et queden una bona quantitat de punts."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:363
#, python-format
msgid "On Track (75-100%% of allowance)"
msgstr "En bon camí (75-100%% de la bonificació)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:365
msgid ""
"You're at or near your daily points limit. Be mindful of remaining points "
"for the day. Consider lower-point food choices."
msgstr ""
"Esteu al límit o a prop del vostre límit de punts diaris. Tingueu en compte "
"els punts restants del dia. Penseu en les opcions d'aliments més baixes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:369
#, python-format
msgid "Over Budget (100-125%% of allowance)"
msgstr "Per sobre del pressupost (100-125%% de la dotació)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:371
msgid ""
"You've exceeded your daily points allowance. Consider using weekly points or"
" making lower-point choices for remaining meals."
msgstr ""
"Heu superat el vostre nombre de punts diaris. Penseu en utilitzar punts "
"setmanals o fer opcions de punts més baixos per als àpats restants."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:375
#, python-format
msgid "Significantly Over (>125%% of allowance)"
msgstr "Significativament per sobre (>125%% de la dotació)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:377
msgid ""
"You've significantly exceeded your daily points. Consider adjusting your "
"food choices, using weekly points, or planning lower-point meals."
msgstr ""
"Heu superat significativament els vostres punts diaris. Penseu en ajustar "
"les vostres opcions d'aliments, utilitzar punts setmanals o planificar àpats"
" de punts més baixos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:387
msgid "Enter the calories from the food's nutrition label"
msgstr "Introduïu les calories de l'etiqueta nutricional de l'aliment"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:388
msgid "Enter the saturated fat content in grams"
msgstr "Introduïu el contingut de greixos saturats en grams"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:389
msgid "Enter the sugar content in grams"
msgstr "Introduïu el contingut de sucre en grams"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:390
msgid "Enter the protein content in grams (protein reduces points)"
msgstr ""
"Introduïu el contingut de proteïnes en grams (les proteïnes redueixen els "
"punts)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:391
msgid "Enter your daily points allowance (typically 23-71 points)"
msgstr ""
"Introduïu la vostra quantitat diària de punts (normalment 23-71 punts)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:392
msgid "Click 'Calculate Points' to see the SmartPoints value"
msgstr "Feu clic a \"Calcula punts\" per veure el valor dels SmartPoints"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:393
msgid ""
"Review the breakdown to understand how each nutrient contributes to the "
"total points"
msgstr ""
"Reviseu el desglossament per entendre com contribueix cada nutrient al total"
" de punts"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:402
msgid "SmartPoints Value"
msgstr "Valor de SmartPoints"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:404
msgid ""
"The total points assigned to the food based on the SmartPoints formula. "
"Lower points indicate healthier, more nutrient-dense choices."
msgstr ""
"El total de punts assignats a l'aliment segons la fórmula de SmartPoints. "
"Els punts més baixos indiquen opcions més saludables i més denses en "
"nutrients."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:410
msgid ""
"Shows how each nutritional component (calories, saturated fat, sugar, "
"protein) contributes to the total points. Protein reduces points, while "
"calories, saturated fat, and sugar increase points."
msgstr ""
"Mostra com cada component nutricional (calories, greixos saturats, sucre, "
"proteïnes) contribueix al total de punts. Les proteïnes redueixen els punts,"
" mentre que les calories, els greixos saturats i el sucre augmenten els "
"punts."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:416
msgid ""
"The points you have left in your daily allowance after consuming this food. "
"This helps you plan your remaining meals and snacks."
msgstr ""
"Els punts que et queden a la teva dieta després de consumir aquest aliment. "
"Això us ajuda a planificar els vostres àpats i berenars restants."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:422
msgid ""
"Indicates whether you're within, at, or over your daily points budget. This "
"helps you make informed decisions about food choices."
msgstr ""
"Indica si estàs dins, en o per sobre del pressupost de punts diaris. Això us"
" ajuda a prendre decisions informades sobre les opcions alimentàries."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:430
msgid "Tips for Managing Points"
msgstr "Consells per gestionar els punts"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Choose foods high in protein to reduce points and stay satisfied longer"
msgstr ""
"Trieu aliments rics en proteïnes per reduir punts i mantenir-vos satisfet "
"durant més temps"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:433
msgid "Limit foods high in saturated fat and sugar, as they add more points"
msgstr ""
"Limiteu els aliments rics en greixos saturats i sucre, ja que afegeixen més "
"punts"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:434
msgid "Plan your meals ahead of time to stay within your daily points"
msgstr ""
"Planifiqueu els vostres àpats amb antelació per mantenir-vos dins dels "
"vostres punts diaris"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:435
msgid "Use weekly points for special occasions or treats"
msgstr "Utilitzeu punts setmanals per a ocasions especials o llaminadures"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:436
msgid ""
"Focus on zero-point foods (fruits, vegetables, lean proteins) to fill up "
"without using points"
msgstr ""
"Centra't en aliments de punt zero (fruites, verdures, proteïnes magres) per "
"omplir sense utilitzar punts"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:437
msgid ""
"Track all foods and beverages throughout the day for accurate point counting"
msgstr ""
"Feu un seguiment de tots els aliments i begudes al llarg del dia per a un "
"recompte de punts precís"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:449
msgid ""
"This calculator uses the Weight Watchers SmartPoints formula. Actual points "
"may vary slightly based on Weight Watchers' official database and any "
"program updates."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta calculadora utilitza la fórmula de Weight Watchers SmartPoints. Els "
"punts reals poden variar lleugerament en funció de la base de dades oficial "
"de Weight Watchers i de qualsevol actualització del programa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:455
msgid ""
"Your daily points allowance is personalized and should be determined through"
" the official Weight Watchers program or app."
msgstr ""
"La vostra quantitat diària de punts és personalitzada i s'ha de determinar "
"mitjançant el programa o l'aplicació oficial Weight Watchers."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:461
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"the official Weight Watchers program, app, or professional guidance. Always "
"consult with Weight Watchers coaches or registered dietitians for "
"personalized guidance."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta calculadora només té finalitats informatives i no ha de substituir "
"el programa, l'aplicació ni l'orientació professional oficial de Weight "
"Watchers. Consulteu sempre amb entrenadors de Weight Watchers o dietistes "
"registrats per obtenir una orientació personalitzada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:467
msgid ""
"Weight Watchers is a registered trademark. This calculator is not affiliated"
" with or endorsed by Weight Watchers International, Inc."
msgstr ""
"Weight Watchers és una marca registrada. Aquesta calculadora no està "
"afiliada ni avalada per Weight Watchers International, Inc."

