#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:210
msgid "What is a Day Counter?"
msgstr "Què és un comptador de dies?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:212
msgid ""
"A day counter is a tool that calculates the number of days between dates, "
"days since a past date, days until a future date, or creates countdowns to "
"specific events. This calculator handles all calendar complexities including"
" leap years, varying month lengths, and year boundaries to provide accurate "
"day counts."
msgstr ""
"Un comptador de dies és una eina que calcula el nombre de dies entre dates, "
"dies des d'una data passada, dies fins a una data futura o crea comptes "
"enrere per a esdeveniments específics. Aquesta calculadora gestiona totes "
"les complexitats del calendari, inclosos els anys de traspàs, la durada "
"variable dels mesos i els límits de l'any per proporcionar un recompte de "
"dies precisos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:219
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Days Between, Days Since, Days "
"Until, or Countdown)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu un tipus de càlcul al menú desplegable (Dies entre, Dies des de,"
" Dies fins o Compte enrere)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:220
msgid "Enter the required dates in the input form."
msgstr "Introduïu les dates requerides al formulari d'entrada."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:221
msgid "For countdown, optionally enter an event name."
msgstr "Per al compte enrere, introduïu opcionalment un nom d'esdeveniment."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:222
msgid "Click 'Count Days' to see the results."
msgstr "Feu clic a \"Comptar dies\" per veure els resultats."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:233
msgid ""
"Calculate the exact number of days between two dates. Includes breakdown "
"into weeks, months, hours, minutes, seconds, and business days."
msgstr ""
"Calcula el nombre exacte de dies entre dues dates. Inclou el desglossament "
"en setmanes, mesos, hores, minuts, segons i dies laborables."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:237
msgid ""
"Calculate how many days have passed since a past date. Useful for tracking "
"time elapsed since events, milestones, or important dates."
msgstr ""
"Calcula quants dies han passat des d'una data passada. Útil per fer un "
"seguiment del temps transcorregut des dels esdeveniments, fites o dates "
"importants."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:241
msgid ""
"Calculate how many days remain until a future date. Perfect for planning, "
"deadlines, and upcoming events."
msgstr ""
"Calcula quants dies queden per a una data futura. Perfecte per a la "
"planificació, els terminis i els propers esdeveniments."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:245
msgid ""
"Create a countdown to a specific event with an optional event name. Shows "
"days, weeks, months, hours, and minutes until the event."
msgstr ""
"Creeu un compte enrere per a un esdeveniment específic amb un nom "
"d'esdeveniment opcional. Mostra dies, setmanes, mesos, hores i minuts fins a"
" l'esdeveniment."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:253
