#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gpa_calculator.html:217
msgid "What is GPA?"
msgstr "Què és el GPA?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gpa_calculator.html:219
msgid ""
"Grade Point Average (GPA) is a numerical representation of a student's "
"academic performance. It is calculated by dividing the total quality points "
"earned by the total credit hours attempted. GPA is used by educational "
"institutions to evaluate student performance, determine academic standing, "
"and make decisions about scholarships, honors, and graduation eligibility."
msgstr ""
"La mitjana de notes (GPA) és una representació numèrica del rendiment "
"acadèmic d'un estudiant. Es calcula dividint el total de punts de qualitat "
"obtinguts pel total d'hores de crèdit intentades. Les institucions "
"educatives utilitzen el GPA per avaluar el rendiment dels estudiants, "
"determinar la posició acadèmica i prendre decisions sobre beques, honors i "
"elegibilitat per a la graduació."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gpa_calculator.html:226
msgid "Select your GPA scale (4.0, 4.3, or 5.0) from the dropdown."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu la vostra escala GPA (4.0, 4.3 o 5.0) al menú desplegable."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gpa_calculator.html:227
msgid "Add courses by clicking the 'Add Course' button."
msgstr "Afegiu cursos fent clic al botó \"Afegeix curs\"."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gpa_calculator.html:228
msgid ""
"Enter the course name, select the grade, and enter the number of credits for"
" each course."
msgstr ""
"Introduïu el nom del curs, seleccioneu la qualificació i introduïu el nombre"
" de crèdits per a cada curs."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gpa_calculator.html:229
msgid ""
"Optionally, enter your current GPA and credits earned to calculate "
